<Script>
  <Scene id="scene_3_3" pageStart="48" pageEnd="49" act="Act 3: Desperate Measures"
    title="The Ambush" description="The Grade 7s attack Greg but are brutally defeated">
    <Page number="48">
      <SceneHeading>The Ambush</SceneHeading>
      <DialogueBlock>
        <Line>We've heard a lot about you, Grade 10er.</Line>
      </DialogueBlock>
      <StageDirection>THE GRADE 7s emerge on their scooters, armed to the teeth.</StageDirection>
      <DialogueBlock>
        <Line>We've gotta admit it, we kind of admire you.</Line>
        <Line>This isn't personal, you know.</Line>
        <Line>We just really like Nandos.</Line>
        <Line>'There's a price on your head.</Line>
        <Line>And I'm hungry for Peri Peri.</Line>
        <Line>Well make it quick.</Line>
      </DialogueBlock>
      <DialogueBlock>
        <Speaker>GREG</Speaker>
        <Line>Oh, please don't.</Line>
      </DialogueBlock>
      <DialogueBlock>
        <Line>Your funeral, dude.</Line>
      </DialogueBlock>
    </Page>
    <Page number="49">
      <StageDirection>GREG laughs.</StageDirection>
      <DialogueBlock>
        <Speaker>GREG</Speaker>
        <Line>Finally.</Line>
      </DialogueBlock>
      <StageDirection>They run at each other as the stage goes dark.</StageDirection>
    </Page>
  </Scene>
</Script>